The Excel interface of Dodoni.net is based on ExcelDNA (http://exceldna.codeplex.com), Copyright (C) 2005-2012 Govert van Drimmelen
Dodoni.net may load several external libraries at run-time, for example
- Basic Linear Algebra Subprograms (BLAS), http://www.netlib.org/blas/ - Linear Algebra Package (LaPack), http://www.netlib.org/lapack/, - Intel Math Kernel Library (MKL), http://software.intel.com/en-us/products/mkl - AMD Math Core Library (ACML), http://developer.amd.com/libraries/acml/ - FFTW library, http://www.fftw.org, Copyright (c) 2003, 2007-8 Matteo Frigo, Copyright (c) 2003, 2007-8 Massachusetts Institute of Technology - NLOpt, http://ab-initio.mit.edu/nlopt, - SwamOps, www.hvass-labs.org
etc. which are under there license.
